<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <h2>New Seller Match Notification</h2>
  <p>Dear {{advisorName}},</p>
  
  <p>Great news! You have been matched with a new potential client through our Advisor-Chooser Platform:</p>
  
  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p><strong>Industry:</strong> {{sellerIndustry}}</p>
    <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{sellerGeography}}</p>
    <p><strong>Annual Revenue:</strong> ${{sellerRevenue}}</p>
  </div>
  
  <p>This match is based on your expertise and service areas.</p>
  
  <p><strong>What to expect:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>The seller may contact you directly via email</li>
    <li>This is a qualified lead based on your profile criteria</li>
    <li>No action is required from you at this time</li>
  </ul>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The Advisor Chooser Platform Team</p>
  
  <hr style="margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
    This is an automated notification. You can manage your lead preferences in your profile settings.
  </p>
</div>